		<section id="share-panel-horiz" class="share-panel instapaper_ignore">
			
			<ul class="buttons">
				<li class="pin-button"><a href="#"></a></li>
				<li class="tweet"><a class="socialite twitter" href="http://twitter.com/share" data-count="none" data-via="remodelista"></a></li>
				<li class="gplus"><a class="socialite googleplus" href="https://plusone.google.com/_/+1/confirm?hl=en" data-annotation="none" data-size="medium"></a></li>
				<li class="fb"><a class="socialite facebook" href="http://www.facebook.com/sharer.php" data-send="true" data-layout="button_count" data-show-faces="false"></a></li>
			</ul><!-- /.buttons -->
				</section><!-- /#share-panel-horiz -->

		<section id="content-body" class="raw">
			
			
			<p>Inspired by the bedrooms in today's <a href="/posts/hotels-lodging-floroom-in-florence">Hotels &amp; Lodging: Floroom in Florence</a>, we rounded up a collection of clean-lined four-poster bed frames&mdash;modern takes on the classic four-poster bed.</p>
<p><img alt="mdf-italia-aluminum-bed.jpg" src="/img/sub/mdf-italia-aluminum-bed.jpg" /></p>
<p>Above: The sleek <a target="_blank" href="http://www.architonic.com/cat/view/1004557">White Lacquered Aluminum Bed</a> with canopy by MDF Italia carries a hefty price tag; locate retailers by zip code at <a target="_blank" href="http://www.architonic.com/cat/view/1004557">Architonic</a>.</p>
<p><img width="372" height="406" alt="portico-canopy-bed.jpg" src="/img/sub/portico-canopy-bed.jpg" /></p>
<p>Above: The <a target="_blank" href="http://www.roomandboard.com/rnb/product/detail.do?productGroup=641&amp;category=rm_bedrooms&amp;subcategory=bed">Stainless Steel Portico Canopy Bed</a> is $1,399 for the queen size at Room &amp; Board.</p>
<p><img width="425" height="425" alt="Edland Bed" src="/img/sub/0098199_pe239139_s4.JPG" /></p>
<p>Above: Ikea's wood <a href="/products/edland-four-poster-bed">Edland Bed</a> is $299 for the queen size.</p>
<p>.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; .<img width="315" height="388" alt="Shaker Four Poster Bed" src="/img/sub/shaker-four-poster-bed.jpg" /></p>
<p>Above: We like the simplicity of the <a target="_blank" href="http://vermontwoodsstudios.com/store/index.php/products/shaker-four-poster-bed">Shaker Four-Poster Bed</a>, available in walnut, cherry, or maple; $2,018 for the queen size at Vermont Wood Studios.</p>
<p><img width="383" height="352" alt="Arkadia Bed" src="/img/sub/arkadia-bed.jpg" /></p>
<p>Above: The custom-made <a href="/products/arkadia-four-poster-bed">Arkadia Four-Poster Bed </a>in solid oak by Ontario-based Claus Pummer Furniture is $3000 for the queen size and is available in several different woods and in whitewash,&nbsp; honey or dark finishes. They ship all over the world; contact Pummer Furniture to order.</p>
			
